OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772582589
OL,3,CUK economy could face 'significant
OL,4,Chit' from war in Middle-East, OBR warns
OL,6,F"My plan is the right one," bellowed
OL,7,Fthe chancellor this lunchtime as she
OL,8,Fguided us through the Office for
OL,9,FBudget Responsibility's updated
OL,10,Fassessment of the UK's economic
OL,11,Fprospects.
OL,13,FThe OBR's forecast shows inflation
OL,14,Ffading, interest rates coming down
OL,15,Ffurther and borrowing falling.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
