OL,3,CUK economy could face 'significant
OL,4,Chit' from war in Middle-East, OBR warns
OL,6,FThe price of oil and gas has already
OL,7,Fsurged well beyond the level the OBR
OL,8,Fassumed going forward, and the stock
OL,9,Fmarket rise, which boosted tax
OL,10,Freceipts, has gone into reverse.
OL,12,FOn the bond markets, the interest
OL,13,Frates charged to governments have
OL,14,Fincreased, for the UK government more
OL,15,Fthan most.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
