OL,3,CUK economy could face 'significant
OL,4,Chit' from war in Middle-East, OBR warns
OL,6,FThe Resolution Foundation calculates
OL,7,Fthat if energy prices remain at the
OL,8,Flevel they have reached, it could add
OL,9,Fover #500 to the typical UK household
OL,10,Fenergy bill in the summer and roughly
OL,11,Fa percentage point to inflation.
OL,13,FIran's attempts to widen the war to
OL,14,Fthe Gulf region are causing havoc.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
