OL,3,CUK economy could face 'significant
OL,4,Chit' from war in Middle-East, OBR warns
OL,6,FThe Strait of Hormuz is all but closed
OL,7,Fto shipping; oil tankers can't reload.
OL,8,FTonight, Iraq says it is preparing to
OL,9,Fshut production in its biggest fields,
OL,10,Fincluding West Qurna. Yesterday, Qatar
OL,11,Fsuspended production of liquefied
OL,12,Fnatural gas.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,19,FIf production stops, it will take time
OL,20,Fto restart.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
