OL,3,CUK economy could face 'significant
OL,4,Chit' from war in Middle-East, OBR warns
OL,6,FWho knows how long the conflict will
OL,7,Flast, but the OBR warned today that
OL,8,Fthe UK economy could face a "very
OL,9,Fsignificant" hit.
OL,11,F"The UK is a major importer of energy,
OL,12,Fso there's nothing good about energy
OL,13,Fprices being higher," says Professor
OL,14,FDavid Miles, chief economist at the
OL,15,FOBR.
OL,26,@pD@]OUqD@LO]sD@AOUuD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
