OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772582589
OL,3,CUK economy could face 'significant
OL,4,Chit' from war in Middle-East, OBR warns
OL,6,F"If we see energy prices rise as much
OL,7,Fagain over the next week and stay
OL,8,Fthere - if that just becomes a new
OL,9,Fnormal, 20, 30, 40% higher energy
OL,10,Fprices - I think that's a material
OL,11,Fimpact on inflation, as it will likely
OL,12,Fget passed through."
OL,14,FIf sustained, a surge in energy prices
OL,15,Fwould leave everyone in the U.K. worse
OL,16,Foff - households, businesses and the
OL,17,Fgovernment.
