OL,3,CUK economy could face 'significant
OL,4,Chit' from war in Middle-East, OBR warns
OL,6,FInvestors have no particular gift of
OL,7,Fforesight, but the market movement
OL,8,Ftoday suggests they are preparing for
OL,9,Fa conflict that could drag on.
